summary: ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE LATER TODAY INTO FRIDAY ON PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS AS JERRY PASSES NEARBY... ...NOAA AND AIR FORCE RESERVE HURRICANE HUNTERS TO INVESTIGATE THE STORM THIS MORNING... As of 5:00 AM AST Thu Oct 09 the center of Jerry was located near 15.7, -57.7 with movement WNW at 20 mph. The minimum central pressure was 999 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
